  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "C. arabica HiFi assembly was carried out with hifiasm v.0.16.1 (ref.",
    "84), followed by scaffolding using Hi-C data from Dovetail technology and ALLHiC 85 pipeline.",
    "Final quality checks and manual adjustments of the assembly were carried out using 3d-DNA 86 and juicebox 87.",
    "The completeness of the different assemblies was assessed using BUSCO v.5.2.2 (ref.",
    "35) with the eudicots_odb10 database (2,326 genes; Table 1)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Final quality checks and manual adjustments of the assembly were carried out using 3d-DNA 86 and juicebox 87."
  ]
